**“Commercial Use”** means any use that directly or indirectly supports commercial activity, business operations, paid work, revenue generation, customer delivery, employee operations, or another commercial benefit.

**“Redistribution”** means making the Software, its source code, its packages, or a substantial portion available to another person or entity, whether for payment or without payment.

**“Competing Product”** means a reusable UI library, component library, design system, data-grid library, application framework, template product, UI builder, low-code or no-code platform, hosted component service, or other product or service with a substantially similar primary purpose.

